    - rid: 4538204733574742306
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Who are you? Why did you break into my house? HELP!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742307
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Sorry, sorry! I'm here to help! I'm looking for chief. Are you his
          wife?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742308
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Oh, I'm sorry, but ever since my husband left, I've been afraid of
          strangers.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742309
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Can you help me? I will pay you if you will find him.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742310
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Calm down, tell me what you know first.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742311
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, so it started before winter.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742312
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I know there was an incident where someone's house was robbed, and
          the first frost was approaching.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742313
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He told me then that he would take care of it and that no one would
          get hurt.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742314
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Winter came, and there were no bad incidents. Even all the transports
          from the city reached the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742315
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I thought he had actually taken care of it until the day he disappeared.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742316
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He was very upset, saying he had no money and needed it. I almost offered
          him what I had set aside.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742317
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: At that moment, a letter appeared under the door. Hendrik read it,
          then threw it in the fireplace and left the house.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742318
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I managed to pull the letter out. Here it is.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742319
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I don't know anything more. Please, find my husband.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204733574742320
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Please, find my husband.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
--- !u!114 &4654312054654717246
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e5800231a05eaae43b00503881229245, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  originalLanguage: en
  translationSets:
  - counter: 19
    languageCode: en
    translations:
    - id: 0
      language: en
      text: Lyra
    - id: 1
      language: en
      text: Who are you? Why did you break into my house? HELP!
    - id: 2
      language: en
      text: Player
    - id: 3
      language: en
      text: 'Sorry, sorry! I''m here to help! I''m looking for chief. Do you know
        him? '
    - id: 4
      language: en
      text: Sorry, sorry! I'm here to help! I'm looking for chief. Are you his wife?
    - id: 5
      language: en
      text: Oh, I'm sorry, since my husband is gone I'm afraid to go out, let alone
        with strangers.
    - id: 6
      language: en
      text: Oh, I'm sorry, but ever since my husband left, I've been afraid of strangers.
    - id: 7
      language: en
      text: Can you help me? I will pay you if you will find him.
    - id: 8
      language: en
      text: Calm down, tell me what you know first.
    - id: 9
      language: en
      text: Okay, so it started before winter.
    - id: 10
      language: en
      text: I know there was an incident where someone's house was robbed, and the
        first frost was approaching.
    - id: 11
      language: en
      text: He told me then that he would take care of it and that no one would get
        hurt.
    - id: 12
      language: en
      text: Winter came, and there were no bad incidents. Even all the transports
        from the city reached the village.
    - id: 13
      language: en
      text: I thought he had actually taken care of it until the day he disappeared.
    - id: 14
      language: en
      text: He was very upset, saying he had no money and needed it. I almost offered
        him what I had set aside.
    - id: 15
      language: en
      text: At that moment, a letter appeared under the door. Hendrik read it, then
        threw it in the fireplace and left the house.
    - id: 16
      language: en
      text: I managed to pull the letter out. Here it is.
    - id: 17
      language: en
      text: I don't know anything more. Please, find my husband.
    - id: 18
      language: en
      text: Please, find my husband.
